<ArticleLayout
  title="Understanding PPM — What It Measures and Where It Confuses People"
  description="PPM measures dissolved solids in your nutrient solution — the same thing as EC, just in different units. Here's what it means, why there are two different scales, and when it matters."
  silo="Equipment & Tools"
  siloSlug="equipment"
